<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/657732-do-we-have-to-read-sea-of-poppies-before">Do we have to read &quot;sea of poppies&#39; before proceeding on to this one? Or can it be read as a standalone?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_657732'><a id="like_count_community_question_657732" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/657732?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">4 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F9783627-river-of-smoke">like</a></span>

