<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    River: The Pearl River. Smoke: the opium that is smuggled by boat along that river. Also (spoiler alert) when the opium is destroyed at the end, it wa<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    River: The Pearl River. Smoke: the opium that is smuggled by boat along that river. Also (spoiler alert) when the opium is destroyed at the end, it washes away into the river. <a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
